<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

   <head>
      <meta charset="UTF-8">
      <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
      <title>Order Confirmation</title>
   </head>

   <body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f2f4f6; padding: 20px; color: #333;">
      <div
         style="max-width: 600px; margin: auto; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; padding: 30px; box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
         <h2 style="color: #2c3e50;">Thank you for your purchase!</h2>
         <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5;">We're happy to confirm your order. Below are your order details:
         </p>

         <table style="width: 100%; margin-top: 20px; border-collapse: collapse;">
            <tr>
               <td style="padding: 10px; font-weight: bold;">Order ID:</td>
               <td style="padding: 10px;">
                  <%= order._id %>
               </td>
            </tr>
            <tr style="background-color: #f9f9f9;">
               <td style="padding: 10px; font-weight: bold;">Course Name:</td>
               <td style="padding: 10px;">
                  <%= order.name %>
               </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
               <td style="padding: 10px; font-weight: bold;">Price:</td>
               <td style="padding: 10px;">$<%= order.price %>
               </td>
            </tr>
            <tr style="background-color: #f9f9f9;">
               <td style="padding: 10px; font-weight: bold;">Order Date:</td>
               <td style="padding: 10px;">
                  <%= order.date %>
               </td>
            </tr>
         </table>

         <p style="margin-top: 30px; font-size: 16px;">You can access your course anytime from your dashboard.</p>

         <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 30px;">
            <a href="https://yourwebsite.com/dashboard"
               style="background-color: #1e90ff; color: #fff; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold;">Go
               to Dashboard</a>
         </div>

         <p style="margin-top: 40px; font-size: 14px; color: #999;">If you have any questions, feel free to contact our
            support team.</p>
      </div>
   </body>

</html>